RESEARCH NOTICE:
This software was developed as part of academic research on occupational health
screening. If you use this software in your research, please cite:

Teng, T.-H., Lee, T.-R., Byeon, S. H., & Choi, M.-T. (2024). 
Binary-Relevance-based Multi-Label Classification using Medical Examination Data 
to Screen for Complex Illnesses in Construction and Manufacturing Workers. 
Journal of KIIT, 22(2), 43-52. doi:10.14801/jkiit.2024.22.2.43

---

DATA USAGE NOTICE:
The medical examination data used in this research is protected under IRB
approval (HS23-3) and is not included in this repository. Users must obtain
their own data with appropriate ethical approvals for medical research.
